
Limit scripts
-------------

CLs script taken from:
https://svnweb.cern.ch/trac/atlasusr/browser/armbrust/runAsymptoticsCLs/trunk

Check there for updated tags

Michel's limit code is here: /cluster/data05/michel/bdtmva/limits
(now migrated here)


How to use the Makefile
-----------------------

To create limits::

    make CHANNEL=comb

    make CHANNEL=lh

    make CHANNEL=mulh

    make CHANNEL=elh

    make CHANNEL=hh

    make CHANNEL=hh MASS=125

you get the idea...

To just create a workspace::

    make workspace CHANNEL=comb

    make workspace CHANNEL=hh MASS=125

you get the idea...
